    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those who prioritize functionality over aesthetics. While the car starts and drives reliably, the engine shows some minor oil seepage and the suspension feels a bit soft, suggesting that some maintenance will be required in the near future. The exterior has several visible scratches, faded paint on the roof, and a few small dings typical of a car this age. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear on the driver's seat and the carpets are stained, but all essential electronics and climate controls remain operational.",
