    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. I\u2019ve babied this car since the day I got it, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in incredible shape, inside and out\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
