    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band and a 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Mechanically, this chassis has been fastidiously maintained; the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed\u2014critical preventative measures for the platform. The suspension geometry remains true with fresh bushings and original dampers, providing the tactile steering feedback these cars are known for. The exterior paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the underside is remarkably clean, showing no signs of corrosion or fluid seepage. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine for the serious driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    }
